HTML: Hypertext markup language

Tags:
<p> opening tage at the beginning of the paragraph
</p> closing tag

Element:
<p>Content.</p>
This is an element (emelemt may or may not contain closing tag)

<p>,<h>,<article>:
<p>Paragraph</p>
<h1>headline</h1>
<article>article.</article>

<em>:
<p>para<em>emphasized</em>paracomplete</p>
<em> emphasized

Example:
<article>
 <h1>headline</h1>
 <p>firstpara</p>
 <p>secondpara</p>
 <p>thirdpara<em>emphasized</em>para</p>
<article>

